title: Landhotel Schlickberg
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, European, Fusion, Austrian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Hotel restaurant. On the menu card are around 5 vegetarian and 5 vegan choices listed. The staff is knowledegable about the dishes. The vegan meals might include tofu, vegan sausage, grilled vegetables, salad and/or pasta.
